22 SPECIAL EDUCATION SERVICES
23 Sec. 401. From the funds appropriated in part 1 for special
24 education operations, the department shall use $100,000.00 to
25 design and distribute to all parents and legal guardians of a
26 student with a disability the following information:
27 (a) Federal and state mandates regarding the rights and
28 protections of students with disabilities, including, but not
29 limited to, individualized education programs to ensure that
STM H01045'25 (H-2) 1ngaew

